sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Notebook/KFP SDK)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant APIServer as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB/MySQL<br/>3306/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller<br/>Namespace-scoped
    participant WorkflowPod as Workflow Pod<br/>Pipeline Task
    participant Storage as Minio/S3<br/>9000/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Persistence as Persistence Agent<br/>Metadata Collector

    Note over User,Persistence: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission via API

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: OAuth
    Route->>OAuth: Forward request<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OpenShift OAuth token
    OAuth->>APIServer: HTTP/8888<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    APIServer->>DB: INSERT pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>APIServer: Confirm
    APIServer->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Argo: Workflow Created Event
    Argo->>Argo: Reconcile Workflow CR
    Argo->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow Pods
    K8sAPI-->>WorkflowPod: Pod Created
    APIServer-->>OAuth: Pipeline Created Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,Persistence: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution and Artifact Storage

    WorkflowPod->>APIServer: Report task status<br/>gRPC/8887<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WorkflowPod->>Storage: Upload artifact<br/>S3 API HTTP/9000 or HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Access/Secret Keys
    Storage-->>WorkflowPod: Artifact stored
    WorkflowPod->>MLMD: Log artifact lineage<br/>gRPC/8080<br/>Optional mTLS
    MLMD-->>WorkflowPod: Metadata recorded
    WorkflowPod->>APIServer: Task completed
    APIServer->>DB: Update run status<br/>MySQL/3306

    Note over Persistence,DB: Flow 3: Persistence Agent

    Persistence->>K8sAPI: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Persistence: Workflow status change
    Persistence->>APIServer: Get workflow details<br/>gRPC/8887<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    APIServer-->>Persistence: Workflow metadata
    Persistence->>DB: Persist execution metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>Persistence: Confirm

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 4: Artifact Retrieval

    User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/artifacts/{id}<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    Route->>OAuth: Forward request
    OAuth->>APIServer: HTTP/8888<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    APIServer->>Storage: Generate signed URL<br/>60s expiry
    Storage-->>APIServer: Signed URL
    APIServer-->>OAuth: Return signed URL
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: Redirect to signed URL
    User->>Storage: Download artifact<br/>Direct access via signed URL
    Storage-->>User: Artifact data

    Note over User,Persistence: Flow 5: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    participant Scheduler as Scheduled Workflow Controller

    Scheduler->>K8sAPI: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Scheduler: Schedule triggered
    Scheduler->>APIServer: Create pipeline run<br/>gRPC/8887<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    APIServer->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR
    K8sAPI-->>Argo: Workflow Created Event
    Argo->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow Pods
